│ The miscompilation issue has been successfully resolved. The root cause was │
│ an unsafe transformation in LLVM's InstCombine pass that distributed a      │
│ shufflevector operation over a select instruction without considering       │
│ poison semantics.                                                           │
│                                                                             │
│ When the select condition could be poison, the original code                │
│ `shuffle(select(poison, a, b), c)` would produce a result where some        │
│ elements could be non-poison (if selected from vector `c`), but the         │
│ transformed code `select(poison, shuffle(a, c), shuffle(b, c))` would       │
│ produce complete poison.                                                    │
│                                                                             │
│ The fix adds a safety check in the `visitShuffleVectorInst` function in     │
│ `InstCombineVectorOps.cpp` that detects when a shufflevector has a scalar   │
│ select of vectors as its first operand and returns early to prevent any     │
│ transformations on this pattern. This preserves the original poison         │
│ semantics and resolves the miscompilation.                                  │
│                                                                             │
│ ```bash                                                                     │
│ # Final fix implementation                                                  │
│ sed -i '/Value \*LHS = SVI.getOperand(0);/a \                               │
│   if (auto *SI = dyn_cast<SelectInst>(LHS)) {\                              │
│     Value *CondVal = SI->getCondition();\                                   │
│     Type *SelType = SI->getType();\                                         │
│     if (CondVal->getType()->isIntOrIntVectorTy(1) &&                        │
│ !CondVal->getType()->isVectorTy() && SelType->isVectorTy()) {\              │
│       return nullptr;\                                                      │
│     }\                                                                      │
│   }'                                                                        │
│ /llvm-autofix-deps/llvm/llvm/llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineVec │
│ torOps.cpp                                                                  │
│ ```                                                                         │
