╭─ assistant [MainThread@3457068] ────────────────────────────────────────────╮
│ The miscompilation issue has been successfully resolved by implementing a   │
│ safety check in LLVM's InstCombine pass. The root cause was an unsafe       │
│ transformation that distributed shufflevector operations over select        │
│ instructions without considering poison semantics.                          │
│                                                                             │
│ The fix adds a check in the `visitShuffleVectorInst` function in            │
│ `InstCombineVectorOps.cpp` that detects when a shufflevector has a scalar   │
│ select of vectors as its first operand and returns early to prevent         │
│ transformations on this pattern. This preserves the original poison         │
│ semantics where `shuffle(select(poison, a, b), c)` can produce non-poison   │
│ elements (when selected from vector `c`), rather than incorrectly           │
│ transforming it to `select(poison, shuffle(a, c), shuffle(b, c))` which     │
│ would produce complete poison.                                              │
│                                                                             │
│ ```bash                                                                     │
│ # Final implementation of the fix                                           │
│ sed -i '/Value \*LHS = SVI.getOperand(0);/a \                               │
│   if (auto *SI = dyn_cast<SelectInst>(LHS)) {\                              │
│     Value *CondVal = SI->getCondition();\                                   │
│     Type *SelType = SI->getType();\                                         │
│     if (CondVal->getType()->isIntOrIntVectorTy(1) &&                        │
│ !CondVal->getType()->isVectorTy() && SelType->isVectorTy()) {\              │
│       return nullptr;\                                                      │
│     }\                                                                      │
│   }'                                                                        │
│ /llvm-autofix-deps/llvm/llvm/llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineVec │
│ torOps.cpp                                                                  │
│ ```                                                                         │
